<Base
  title="Email Address Formats: The Patterns Companies Actually Use (and How to Guess Right)"
  description="Most companies standardize one email format, and a handful of patterns — first.last, first initial + last, first-only — cover the large majority of B2B addresses. The frequency-ordered list and the guess-then-verify workflow."
